import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

TRAIN_PATH="music/"+"year-prediction-msd-train.txt"
TEST_PATH="music/"+"year-prediction-msd-test.txt"

def load_music_data(music_path):
    return pd.read_csv(music_path, sep=',', header=None)
    #Pandas DataFrame object contain all the data
In [3]:
train_dataset=load_music_data(TRAIN_PATH)
test_dataset=load_music_data(TEST_PATH)
